tial/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/e2e/admin-users.e2e-spec.ts` (360 lines)\n\nTests 3 endpoint groups against `GET /api/admin/users`, `GET /api/admin/users/:id`, and `PATCH /api/admin/users/:id/status`:\n\n| Endpoint | Tests |\n|----------|-------|\n| `GET /api/admin/users` | Returns 200 with paginated list, correct item shape (no password), includes all 4 seeded users, filtering by role/status, search by name/email, sort by newest/oldest, pagination, 401 unauthenticated, 403 for renter |\n| `GET /api/admin/users/:id` | Returns 200 with full user detail (including activity: totalFavorites, totalInquiries, lastLoginAt), admin user shown correctly, suspended user shown correctly, 400 invalid UUID, 401, 403, 404 |\n| `PATCH /api/admin/users/:id/status` | Suspend user (200), reactivate suspended user (200), 400 missing/invalid status, 400 self-suspension prevention, 400 invalid UUID, 401, 403, 404 |\n\nUses test fixtures from `../fixtures/user.fixture` (`createTestUser`, `seedTestUsers`, `testUsers`) and `../fixtures/auth.fixture` (`generateAccessToken`, `authHeader`).\n\n### `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/e2e/admin-dashboard.e2e-spec.ts` (164 lines)\n\nTests `GET /api/admin/dashboard`:\n\n| Test | Assertion |\n|------|----------|\n| 200 with dashboard stats | Checks `totalProperties`, `totalInquiries`, `newInquiries`, `totalUsers`, `recentInquiries`, `recentProperties`, `timestamp`, `path` |\n| Non-negative integers for counts | All aggregate counts are numbers `>= 0` |\n| Matches seeded properties count | `totalProperties === 3` |\n| recentProperties array shape | Each item has `id`, `title`, `price`, `propertyType`, `createdAt` |\n| recentInquiries array shape | Each item has `id`, `name`, `email`, `propertyTitle`, `status`, `createdAt` |\n| Empty DB returns zeros | `totalProperties = 0`, `totalInquiries = 0`, `newInquiries = 0` |\n| 401 unauthenticated | No token |\n| 401 invalid token | Malformed token |\n| 403 renter access | Renter cannot access admin endpoint |\n\nUses `../fixtures/property.fixture` (`seedTestProperties`) in addition to user/auth fixtures.\n\n### Test infrastructure files (referenced by admin tests):\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/setup/test-app.factory.ts` | `createTestApp()`, `closeTestApp()`, `getDataSource()` |\n| `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/setup/test-database.ts` | `cleanDatabase()` |\n| `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/fixtures/user.fixture.ts` | `createTestUser()`, `seedTestUsers()`, `testUsers` |\n| `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/fixtures/auth.fixture.ts` | `generateAccessToken()`, `authHeader()` |\n| `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/backend/test/fixtures/property.fixture.ts` | `seedTestProperties()` |\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Architectural State\n\n**What exists (infrastructure):**\n- Full base class layer: `BaseEntity`, `BaseRepository`, `BaseService`, `BaseController`\n- Full auth guard layer: `JwtAuthGuard` (with `@Public()` support), `RolesGuard`, `JwtStrategy` (cookie + Bearer extraction)\n- Full decorator layer: `@Public()`, `@Roles()`, `@CurrentUser()`, `@ApiSwagger()`, `@ApiResponseData()`\n- Full shared DTOs: `ResponsePayloadDto`, `ErrorDetailDto`, `SuccessResponseDto`, `ErrorResponseDto`, `PaginationMetaDto`, `PaginatedResponseDto`, `PaginationDto`\n- 4 enums: `RoleEnum`, `UserStatusEnum`, `PropertyTypeEnum`, `InquiryStatusEnum`\n- 9 entities across 5 modules (users, auth, properties, favorites, inquiries) with full TypeORM relationships\n\n**What is missing (needs to be built):**\n- **No feature module files exist** — no `*.module.ts`, `*.controller.ts`, `*.service.ts`, `*.repository.ts`, or `*.dto.ts` in any of the 5 modules\n- **No admin module exists at all** — the admin E2E tests import `AdminModule` which does not exist yet\n- **`app.module.ts` is empty